OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1780510265
OL,3,CGang who abused teenage girl over four-
OL,4,Cyear period jailed for 188 years
OL,6,FA survivor says she was "consumed for
OL,7,F20 years" by the impact of child
OL,8,Fsexual abuse she was subjected to by a
OL,9,Fring of men in Bradford.
OL,11,FThe woman spoke out on Wednesday as
OL,12,Fshe saw a gang of 15 men jailed for
OL,13,Fmore than 180 years collectively for
OL,14,F88 counts of rape over a period of
OL,15,Ffour years.
OL,17,FThe abuse occurred between 2007 and
OL,18,F2011 when the victim was aged between
OL,19,F14 and 18.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1780510265
OL,3,CGang who abused teenage girl over four-
OL,4,Cyear period jailed for 188 years
OL,6,FShe said the men took away her
OL,7,Fchildhood, adding that she would carry
OL,8,Fthe trauma for the rest of her life.
OL,10,FPolice identified her as a potential
OL,11,Fvictim at the end of 2015 after
OL,12,Fnoticing she had been the subject of
OL,13,Fmultiple missing person reports at the
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,FDetectives then launched a full
OL,17,Finvestigation in early 2016 and a
OL,18,Fnumber of men were subsequently
OL,19,Fcharged.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1780510265
OL,3,CGang who abused teenage girl over four-
OL,4,Cyear period jailed for 188 years
OL,6,FThe case was split into multiple
OL,7,Ftrials, with reporting restrictions
OL,8,Fimposed - meaning no details could be
OL,9,Freported until all had been concluded.
OL,11,FA judge at Bradford Crown Court lifted
OL,12,Fthe restrictions on Wednesday, jailing
OL,13,Fthe 15 men to a combined 188 years .
OL,15,FSpeaking out, the victim said: "The
OL,16,Fmen involved have taken more away from
OL,17,Fme than what I can ever describe in
OL,18,Fwords and looking back now I feel sad
OL,19,Ffor my 12-year-old self knowing what
OL,20,Fwas to come.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1780510265
OL,3,CGang who abused teenage girl over four-
OL,4,Cyear period jailed for 188 years
OL,6,F"All in all, this has consumed my life
OL,7,Ffor just short of 20 years, it is not
OL,8,Fsomething which I can forget.
OL,10,F"My childhood has been taken away from
OL,11,Fme, the impact from what I suffered
OL,12,Fduring my teens will always live with
OL,13,Fme and I will carry that every day and
OL,14,Flearn to navigate my way through life
OL,15,Fwith that."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1780510265
OL,3,CGang who abused teenage girl over four-
OL,4,Cyear period jailed for 188 years
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Vicky
OL,7,FGreenbank of Bradford District Police
OL,8,Fsaid: "We welcome the convictions and
OL,9,Fthe sentences today for what has been
OL,10,Fa long time coming for the survivor in
OL,11,Fthis case.
OL,13,F"I would like to commend her courage
OL,14,Fand bravery that she has shown
OL,15,Fthroughout the investigation and the
OL,16,Fcourt process.
OL,18,F"These men horrifically abused a child
OL,19,Ffor their own sexual gratification,
OL,20,Fwhat they did was abhorrent and they
OL,21,Fdeserve to be in jail for a long time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1780510265
OL,3,CGang who abused teenage girl over four-
OL,4,Cyear period jailed for 188 years
OL,6,F"This has been a long and complex
OL,7,Finvestigation resulting in multiple
OL,8,Ftrials, I hope today's outcome will
OL,9,Fgive the victim some closure and a
OL,10,Fsense of justice.
OL,12,F"I hope these convictions give
OL,13,Fconfidence to anyone who has suffered
OL,14,Fabuse, no matter how long ago, to come
OL,15,Fforward and report it. We will listen
OL,16,Fto you, and we will ensure that your
OL,17,Freport is fully investigated."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
